Package managers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationManager
    The application manager class interacts with the entities job and application and allows the addition and withdrawal of job applications in the system.
    JobManager
    The job manager will deal with holding all the jobs in the system and adding and removing any jobs that are needed
    ReportManager
    ReportManager communicates with other classes to generate a readable report containing information pertaining to job postings.
    SignUpManager
    The sign up manager will deal with the sign up process of the system and hold the applicants of the system
    Timer
    Timer will keep track of current date and provide time signals to other manager classes.
